text: Moataz () is an Arabic surname and given name. Notable people with this name include: ==Given name== * Moataz Bellah Abdel-Fattah, Egyptian professor * Moataz Ben Amer, Libyan footballer * Moataz Eno, Egyptian footballer * Mootaz Jounaidi, Lebanese footballer * Moataz Yaseen, Jordanian footballer ==Surname== * Hana Moataz, Egyptian squash player
title: Moataz
